{"tid":876622,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為一次女朋友接收工，見盡人情冷暖，世途險惡","createTime":"2018-10-25T17:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T13:55:13.000Z","uid":92908,"like":50,"dislike":1838,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa5c20678c0212e51835e6e373c611c41ff0e19","tid":876622,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日番番下工見到女友whatsapp，嘩，咁好死搵我食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我話我會夜放，佢就話接我收工仲買野比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/010151_e5b94895233917508a6648cdf4fe805f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F010151_e5b94895233917508a6648cdf4fe805f.png&h=9ef11398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知原來「友朋自遠方來，非奸即盗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（唔好問我點解我放10點，佢8點幾就買野食，可能佢想我食石頭）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/010316_f160d65dd02ca14b8f6632f1a655e2df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F010316_f160d65dd02ca14b8f6632f1a655e2df.png&h=ba9321fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（遲d會一齊去旅行）<br />\n<br />\n另一邊箱，公司有條鬼佬應該要做既野，一句話放工就乜都唔撚理，身為亞洲人，真係覺得好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，鬼佬工作節奏就係咁，放工真係唔撚洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但如果香港工作節奏，你試下一放工時間就唔理d野，屎都有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我唔會怨，我只係會希望下世識得投胎好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/011204_4f7d8f28c1380fadb4445fcebeb7b2b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F011204_4f7d8f28c1380fadb4445fcebeb7b2b3.png&h=9dd3b5a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呀我係社畜，做埋佢d野，因為如果d野唔做埋，賴嘢嗰個都係我，所以我女朋友拎左個Burger比我，我同佢食左一陣就遣返左佢走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解佢咁順攤，未拎到本passport就走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哦，因為原來佢黎搵我既途中已經收到警局通知，有人拎到佢張身分證，聽日可以拎番，所以佢唔需要本passport搞網上身分證手續。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好快，我就收到老闆既whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/011720_441f12d6940289a99dce637d90fd193d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F011720_441f12d6940289a99dce637d90fd193d.png&h=ee69cee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老闆似乎講左句「I know that feel」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勿相認，認到都唔好放上whatsapp group</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<br />\n正評：抵喇，畜社，一張戲飛搞掂你<br />\n負皮：嘩，女朋友對你又好，老闆對你又好，你真係人生大贏家"},{"pid":"4bb4621b06e6d03ef6afaa4f4d5b0c20e50acdaf","tid":876622,"uid":10536,"like":1042,"dislike":2,"score":1040,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:41:01.000Z","msg":"你老細起碼留意到你ot 關心下你已經好難得"},{"pid":"593136743f6640a6f9cc6c32c968a4ba9abddccf","tid":876622,"uid":201604,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:41:52.000Z","msg":"冇女朋友"},{"pid":"779d55aa3c39329ee368b421eda49a25432fe6d5","tid":876622,"uid":92908,"like":2,"dislike":32,"score":-30,"quote":{"pid":"4bb4621b06e6d03ef6afaa4f4d5b0c20e50acdaf","tid":876622,"uid":10536,"like":1042,"dislike":2,"score":1040,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:41:01.000Z","msg":"你老細起碼留意到你ot 關心下你已經好難得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"麻煩比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb135378302025b76c5e7571947bb4988847879","tid":876622,"uid":61989,"like":232,"dislike":2,"score":230,"citedBy":0,"replyT